  "description": "Wavetable (Metallic bank) acts as FM modulator for a Saw carrier at fmDepth 0.55 \u2014 the exact ratio where inharmonic partials tip into bell-like shimmer without breaking into noise. Proc2 is a Wavefolder that further sculpts the FM sidebands. The result is a metallic bloom: warm below 800 Hz, crystalline above. An Envelope LFO routes to wtPos so the wavetable position morphs through the FM attack \u2014 each note is a different alloy.",
